Button 3 to 1 pin
Button 4 to 1 pin
Encoder 1 to 3 pins
Setup comms to robot
Loop
Switch 1 inputs position sends data to robot
Switch 2 inputs position sends data to robot
Switch 3 inputs position sends data to robot
Switch 4 inputs position sends data to robot
Switch 5 inputs position sends data to robot
Switch 6 inputs position sends data to robot
Switch 7 inputs position sends data to robot
Switch 8 inputs position sends data to robot
Gimbal 1 collects positions from encoders, translates position to percentages, then sends data to robot
Gimbal 2 collects positions from encoders, translates position to percentages, then sends data to robot
Trim switch 1 modifies percentage values
Trim switch 2 modifies percentage values
Trim switch 3 modifies percentage values
Trim switch 4 modifies percentage values
LCD displays information from robot plus trim adjustment
Button 1 and button 2 will navigate through menus
Button 3 will be used as shortcut key
Button 4 will be used to select
Encoder 1 shows position and gives values to menu

